{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"21117127b6","title":"中央关于印发清理“中层”“内层”问题的指示的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"87b52f435b","index":0,"year":1951,"month":5,"day":21,"articleId":"21117127b6"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"aebc16589b","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"21117127b6","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央1951年5月21日关于清理“中层”“内层”问题的指示。指示要求在1951年夏秋两季，采用整风方式，有计划、有步骤地对机关工作人员普遍地初步地加以清理，以便弄清情况，处理一些最突出的问题，提高我们组织的纯洁性。指示对清理的范围和重点，步骤和方法，对各类人员处理的政策，工作中注意防止的偏向，以及清理工作的领导问题，都作出了规定。"}],"contents":[{"id":"16bee016d2","type":"title","text":"中央关于印发清理“中层”“内层问题的指示的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"21117127b6"},{"id":"aebc16589b","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央局，各大军区党委，志愿军党委，并转分局，省市区党委，地委及县委，省级军区，军分区，兵团及军师党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"21117127b6"},{"id":"22d56f8ae0","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将中央关于清理“中层”“内层”问题的指示“发给你们，请你们照此执行为要。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"21117127b6"},{"id":"2f83576005","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"21117127b6"},{"id":"68b9ff3829","type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"21117127b6"}],"page":{"id":"b7814da562","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"21117127b6","start":321,"end":321}}}},"__N_SSG":true}